50
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:38,825
Ineuidang, you gave me the chills.

51
00:02:38,909 --> 00:02:43,538
Although no one in my family
has had cancer,

52
00:02:43,622 --> 00:02:46,458
both my mom's and dad's families
have a history

53
00:02:46,541 --> 00:02:48,251
of cerebrovascular and heart issues.

54
00:02:48,335 --> 00:02:49,670
Wow!

55
00:02:50,587 --> 00:02:51,880
See? I told you.

56
00:02:51,963 --> 00:02:52,964
Right.

57
00:02:55,217 --> 00:02:57,678
I guess they can really tell.

58
00:03:00,389 --> 00:03:04,476
My mother has diabetes
and high blood pressure,

59
00:03:04,559 --> 00:03:06,937
and my grandma struggled

60
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:09,272
with cerebrovascular issues for decades.

61
00:03:09,356 --> 00:03:10,357
Oh…

62
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:14,027
I wanted to applaud you
for seeing my family's medical history.

63
00:03:14,111 --> 00:03:15,737
- Thank you.
- Good for you.

64
00:03:15,821 --> 00:03:17,781
You're good. Really good.

65
00:03:18,782 --> 00:03:20,409
That's a shaman for you.

66
00:03:24,454 --> 00:03:26,832
Lee Sobin survived.

67
00:03:26,915 --> 00:03:29,292
On her first try.

68
00:03:29,376 --> 00:03:32,170
- You're right. On her first try.
- One shot, one kill.

69
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:34,798
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

70
00:03:35,549 --> 00:03:37,676
She did it in one go.

71
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:40,762
She's someone who delivers when it counts.

72
00:03:40,846 --> 00:03:43,932
She's not a shaman of many words.

73
00:03:44,015 --> 00:03:47,227
She only said what she had to and left.
That was pretty cool.

74
00:03:48,145 --> 00:03:50,730
I have a feeling she'll keep advancing.

75
00:03:52,732 --> 00:03:54,568
- How cute!
- Oh.

76
00:03:55,152 --> 00:03:56,445
Oh, she's dancing.

77
00:03:57,988 --> 00:04:01,741
Well, there's no beating the shamans.

78
00:04:05,287 --> 00:04:06,872
Here is the next question.

79
00:04:08,123 --> 00:04:10,167
We've got someone else coming out.

80
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:11,543
They look like a couple.

81
00:04:12,043 --> 00:04:14,004
They're a couple.

82
00:04:14,629 --> 00:04:17,215
Oh, is it about love at last?

83
00:04:17,966 --> 00:04:21,094
-Like a compatibility reading?
-Is it about marriage?

84
00:04:25,724 --> 00:04:27,476
No. They don't look too close.

85
00:04:28,393 --> 00:04:31,188
This couple loved passionately

86
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:33,023
for about 3 months,

87
00:04:33,106 --> 00:04:34,941
but they have since separated.

88
00:04:35,025 --> 00:04:36,735
- What?
- Whoa.

89
00:04:36,818 --> 00:04:37,819
Oh?

90
00:04:37,903 --> 00:04:39,446
- Oh, my word.
- Wow.

91
00:04:39,529 --> 00:04:41,156
- What?
- It's shocking they're here.

92
00:04:41,239 --> 00:04:43,200
- They're exes.
- Exactly.

93
00:04:43,283 --> 00:04:44,576
- They broke up.
- What the heck?

94
00:04:46,453 --> 00:04:49,915
Please figure out
whether they're willing to reunite.

95
00:04:49,998 --> 00:04:51,166
DO THEY WANT TO GET BACK TOGETHER?

96
00:04:54,669 --> 00:04:57,798
It'd be crazy if they're here even though
1 of them doesn't want to reconcile.

97
00:04:57,881 --> 00:05:01,843
But it's possible that they
both want to get back together.

98
00:05:01,927 --> 00:05:04,554
- Or neither of them wants to.
- That's right.

99
00:05:05,138 --> 00:05:07,265
This could be really awkward for them.

100
00:05:10,644 --> 00:05:12,979
INEUIDANG
3-YEAR SHAMAN

101
00:05:13,063 --> 00:05:15,524
YOUNG MASTER BYEOLSANG
11-YEAR SHAMAN

102
00:05:19,361 --> 00:05:20,487
This is hard.

103
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,783
I hate reconciling couples.

104
00:05:24,866 --> 00:05:27,661
YOON DAEMAN
5-YEAR SHAMAN

105
00:05:27,744 --> 00:05:30,580
Tell me about Hwang Uchan,
born in the year 1993.

106
00:05:31,081 --> 00:05:35,126
For us, a breakup meant it was over.
But youngsters these days…

107
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:37,087
A lot of them try tarot reading
to see if they should reconcile.

108
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:38,171
Mmm.

109
00:05:38,255 --> 00:05:40,549
If they should reconcile
or end it for good.

110
00:05:41,132 --> 00:05:43,301
It's amazing. We'd decide on our own.

111
00:05:43,385 --> 00:05:45,345
It's impressive they actually came here.

112
00:05:45,428 --> 00:05:47,389
That's Gen Z for you.

113
00:05:48,098 --> 00:05:50,058
This topic is my specialty.

114
00:05:50,141 --> 00:05:51,601
MONAD
8-YEAR TAROT MASTER

115
00:05:51,685 --> 00:05:55,230
The thing most people ask about
when they come to me

116
00:05:55,313 --> 00:05:56,773
