117
00:05:56,857 --> 00:05:59,901
This question was exactly about that,

118
00:05:59,985 --> 00:06:03,321
so I thought it would be a fun one.

119
00:06:04,114 --> 00:06:08,118
I've seen Monad read tarot cards.

120
00:06:08,201 --> 00:06:12,664
Her readings are very detailed.

121
00:06:15,375 --> 00:06:19,296
- Kookjoo's good at relationship readings.
- It's her specialty.

122
00:06:19,963 --> 00:06:24,676
