-Back when we did Comedy Big League,

123
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,928
- she read for us in the green room.
- Right?

124
00:06:27,596 --> 00:06:30,307
-Was she any good?
-She matched a lot of couples up.

125
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,017
- She's good.
- Is she?

126
00:06:33,184 --> 00:06:34,394
LEE KOOKJOO
5-YEAR TAROT MASTER

127
00:06:34,477 --> 00:06:36,104
I can't lose if it's about dating.

128
00:06:36,187 --> 00:06:38,815
I always loved going to tarot masters.

129
00:06:38,899 --> 00:06:40,400
It was so much fun.

130
00:06:40,483 --> 00:06:43,278
All the tarot card categories.

131
00:06:43,361 --> 00:06:45,655
I memorized them in 2 days.

132
00:06:46,239 --> 00:06:49,242
When it comes to tarot reading
about relationships, I'm second to none.

133
00:06:49,326 --> 00:06:51,828
I think it's time to prove myself.

134
00:06:53,038 --> 00:06:54,623
I was kind of seeing someone.

135
00:06:54,706 --> 00:06:56,499
Things didn't work out,

136
00:06:56,583 --> 00:06:58,585
but Kookjoo said we'd get back in touch
at a certain time,

137
00:06:58,668 --> 00:07:01,129
and we really did.

138
00:07:01,212 --> 00:07:03,798
I was impressed that she got that.

139
00:07:03,882 --> 00:07:06,134
I read about love and relationships

140
00:07:06,217 --> 00:07:08,678
by focusing and asking questions.

141
00:07:08,762 --> 00:07:11,556
First, I shuffle the deck
while looking at the person.

142
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,141
Then I keep asking.

143
00:07:13,224 --> 00:07:16,019
Do they have a chance?

144
00:07:16,102 --> 00:07:18,938
If they break up,
will they meet someone else?

145
00:07:19,022 --> 00:07:20,482
"How do they feel?"

146
00:07:21,066 --> 00:07:22,400
I ask questions endlessly.

147
00:07:24,944 --> 00:07:26,529
The 2 people's new relationship.

148
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:34,037
The time is up.

149
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,581
Any Fate Reader who wants to have a go,

150
00:07:36,665 --> 00:07:38,625
press your button now.

151
00:07:40,377 --> 00:07:41,628
- Gosh.
- Of course.

152
00:07:46,716 --> 00:07:48,802
A lot of tarot masters went for it.

153
00:07:48,885 --> 00:07:50,261
This is their specialty.

154
00:07:50,345 --> 00:07:54,057
Here are the 7 Fate Readers
who will present

155
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:56,101
