-Please. Just this once.

156
00:07:56,685 --> 00:07:58,353
SEORIHWA
5-YEAR SHAMAN

157
00:07:58,436 --> 00:07:59,729
Oh!

158
00:08:00,063 --> 00:08:01,648
MONAD
8-YEAR TAROT MASTER

159
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:03,024
Please. Yes!

160
00:08:03,108 --> 00:08:04,150
Lee Kookjoo.

161
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:09,072
The first to press the button,
Seorihwa. Please present your reading.

162
00:08:09,656 --> 00:08:11,282
- Seorihwa.
- The North Korean shaman.

163
00:08:12,951 --> 00:08:19,499
I was born in Hamhung,
Hamgyongnam-do, North Korea.

164
00:08:19,582 --> 00:08:23,795
The shamans here say
they get a lot of good energy

165
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:26,339
after praying on Mount Baekdu.

166
00:08:26,423 --> 00:08:29,259
I was born there,
where Mount Baekdu's energy flows,

167
00:08:29,342 --> 00:08:32,095
so I still have that Mount Baekdu energy
in my bones.

168
00:08:32,178 --> 00:08:33,513
My spiritual power is still at its peak.

169
00:08:34,347 --> 00:08:36,933
If I fail to show my spiritual power,

170
00:08:37,016 --> 00:08:40,061
I should quit being a shaman.

171
00:08:41,104 --> 00:08:43,022
First of all,

172
00:08:43,106 --> 00:08:45,108
as for the man,

173
00:08:45,191 --> 00:08:48,319
