sparkly, and meets many people.

181
00:09:07,756 --> 00:09:09,799
She's right about the woman.

182
00:09:09,883 --> 00:09:11,342
- She's on TV?
- A Miss Korea participant.

183
00:09:11,426 --> 00:09:12,594
- Miss Korea?
- Yes.

184
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:16,264
The woman is

185
00:09:16,347 --> 00:09:18,725
very opinionated and has big dreams.

186
00:09:18,808 --> 00:09:20,643
I say neither of them wants to reconcile.

187
00:09:20,727 --> 00:09:22,353
- Neither of them?
- That's right.

188
00:09:22,437 --> 00:09:23,521
SEORIHWA
NEITHER WANTS TO RECONCILE

189
00:09:23,605 --> 00:09:26,691
