- It's not meant to be.

190
00:09:26,775 --> 00:09:28,651
Next, Monad.

191
00:09:29,652 --> 00:09:31,446
I wonder what Monad will say.

192
00:09:32,614 --> 00:09:35,533
I picked out some cards,
and there are no negative cards

193
