194
00:09:38,495 --> 00:09:40,497
Uh…

195
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:42,749
I don't think they broke up
because they wanted to.

196
00:09:42,832 --> 00:09:45,043
I think there was some sort of condition.

197
00:09:45,126 --> 00:09:47,295
- To put it simply, maybe the woman
- Oh.

198
00:09:47,378 --> 00:09:52,133
went somewhere else to study.

199
00:09:53,384 --> 00:09:55,929
-Yes. To become a journalist.
-Yes, right.

200
00:09:56,012 --> 00:09:57,972
They couldn't meet often,

201
00:09:58,056 --> 00:10:01,351
so they said if they're both single
when they meet again,

202
00:10:01,434 --> 00:10:04,938
they would consider getting back together.

203
00:10:05,021 --> 00:10:08,066
Neither of them has found

204
00:10:08,149 --> 00:10:11,069
