205
00:10:11,152 --> 00:10:13,947
I read the cards
to see if they'd reconcile.

206
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,783
A family forms, and it grows in number.

207
00:10:16,866 --> 00:10:18,910
If they both agree,

208
00:10:18,993 --> 00:10:20,286
not only will they reconcile,

209
00:10:20,370 --> 00:10:24,374
but they could even take a step further.

210
00:10:24,457 --> 00:10:26,126
BIRTH OF AN OFFSPRING,
HEALTH, GOOD OUTCOME

211
00:10:26,709 --> 00:10:29,087
If they were to patch things up,

212
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:33,341
I think they'll get pregnant right away
and get married.

213
00:10:33,424 --> 00:10:37,137
Yes, that's it. She's right.

214
00:10:37,846 --> 00:10:39,222
It's so identical to mine.

215
00:10:39,806 --> 00:10:43,017
So the woman wants to reconcile
if conditions are met.

216
00:10:43,101 --> 00:10:45,228
- And the man also wants to.
- Yes.

217
00:10:45,311 --> 00:10:47,564
MONAD
BOTH WANT TO RECONCILE

218
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:50,900
