219
00:10:52,402 --> 00:10:55,738
Next, Lee Kookjoo.
Please present your reading.

220
00:10:56,281 --> 00:10:58,825
- I wonder what she'll say.
- It's Kookjoo's turn.

221
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:00,869
She looked very confident.

222
00:11:02,162 --> 00:11:06,082
