225
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:11,421
For the man,

226
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:13,923
I got the Ace of Cups.

227
00:11:14,007 --> 00:11:15,133
ACE OF CUPS
THE BEGINNING OF LOVE

228
00:11:15,216 --> 00:11:17,385
It means emotions are overflowing.

229
00:11:17,468 --> 00:11:20,221
It seems he loves her a lot,

230
00:11:20,305 --> 00:11:24,893
but she thinks it's over.

231
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:29,063
As for the man, I kept getting cards

232
00:11:29,147 --> 00:11:31,399
