233
00:11:31,482 --> 00:11:33,651
He needs this woman.

234
00:11:33,735 --> 00:11:36,237
LONELINESS
SIX OF PENTACLES: LACK OF RESOURCES

235
00:11:36,321 --> 00:11:37,572
For the woman,

236
00:11:37,655 --> 00:11:39,532
I got Nine of Cups,

237
00:11:39,616 --> 00:11:41,326
which means she's self-satisfied.

238
00:11:41,409 --> 00:11:43,620
She thinks she can meet someone else

239
00:11:43,703 --> 00:11:45,955
