with this guy.

240
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:49,876
I think he loves her more
and wants to get back together.

241
00:11:49,959 --> 00:11:51,544
As for the woman,

242
00:11:52,045 --> 00:11:53,421
I'm sorry to say this,

243
00:11:53,504 --> 00:11:57,550
but it seems she's ready
to meet someone new.

244
00:11:58,134 --> 00:11:59,677
I think Kookjoo will advance.

245
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,013
I think she's right.

246
00:12:02,096 --> 00:12:04,182
They all do tarot,
but the readings are so different.

247
00:12:08,728 --> 00:12:09,812
The survivor is…

248
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,732
I say neither of them wants to reconcile.

249
00:12:12,815 --> 00:12:13,816
SEORIHWA
NEITHER WANTS TO RECONCILE

250
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,985
- And the man also wants to.
- Yes.

251
00:12:16,069 --> 00:12:17,070
MONAD
BOTH WANT TO RECONCILE

252
00:12:17,153 --> 00:12:21,449
It seems she's ready to meet someone new.

253
00:12:24,118 --> 00:12:25,161
The survivor is…

254
00:12:26,829 --> 00:12:28,248
- Lee Kookjoo.
- Oh!

255
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:30,416
LEE KOOKJOO SURVIVES

256
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:32,710
- Gosh, I can't believe this.
